genresAdvancedInfo.name: rotterdam indie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Rotterdam indie is a genre of music that originated in the Netherlands. It is characterized by its unique blend of indie rock and electronic music. This genre often features upbeat rhythms and catchy melodies that are perfect for dancing. Rotterdam indie has gained a following in the Netherlands and beyond, with many bands and artists creating their own take on this exciting genre.
